NAME
  alint - lint Lua files

SYNOPSIS
  alint [--fix] [--watch] <file.lua> [...]

DESCRIPTION
  Reports syntax errors, undefined-name reads and unused locals (via Aurora's
  AST analyzer) plus implicit globals and trailing whitespace (regex linter).
  Exit code: 0 clean, 1 warnings, 2 errors.

OPTIONS
  --fix     auto-format the file in place, then report findings that still need
            manual attention
  --watch   re-lint whenever a file changes until interrupted (Ctrl-Alt-C)

EXAMPLES
  alint bin/foo.lua
  alint --fix bin/foo.lua
  alint --watch lib/*.lua
